<h1>Radiant 1.0.0 Release Candidate 2</h1>

<script type="text/javascript" src="http://www.haloscan.com/load/radiantcms"></script>
<div class="info">Posted by Jim Gay on Wednesday, June 01, 2011 | <a href="javascript:HaloScan('blog-radiant-1-0-0-release-candidate-2');" target="_self"><script type="text/javascript">postCount('blog-radiant-1-0-0-release-candidate-2');</script></a> | <a href="javascript:HaloScanTB('blog-radiant-1-0-0-release-candidate-2');" target="_self"><script type="text/javascript">postCountTB('blog-radiant-1-0-0-release-candidate-2');</script></a></div>

<p>Thank you to everyone that&#8217;s been helping out with this release.</p>
<p>If you&#8217;ve got a site or extension, please begin testing against this release. As always, report any problems or feature requests at <a href="https://github.com/radiant/radiant/issues">https://github.com/radiant/radiant/issues</a></p>
<p><code>gem install radiant --pre</code> and you&#8217;re on you way!</p>
<div id="extended">

